00:58:00,101 --> 00:58:01,895
You made all these for me.

756
00:58:04,355 --> 00:58:06,900
You kept them all this time?
I'm touched.

757
00:58:10,069 --> 00:58:13,072
Of course, I did.
They're from you. Good night.

758
00:58:15,658 --> 00:58:16,951
Good night to you, too.

759
00:58:30,924 --> 00:58:32,342
Hey, Na-bi.

760
00:58:33,259 --> 00:58:34,677
-Hello.
-Oh, hello.

761
00:58:43,353 --> 00:58:44,729
Did you sleep well?

762
00:58:44,812 --> 00:58:47,815
-Yeah. And you?
-Me too.

763
00:58:47,899 --> 00:58:49,234
-Shall we?
-Yeah.

764
00:59:16,844 --> 00:59:18,096
Careful.

765
00:59:36,239 --> 00:59:37,490
Here, let me.

766
00:59:41,828 --> 00:59:43,496
-Uh, excuse me, sir?
-Yeah?

767
00:59:43,580 --> 00:59:44,747
Would you mind watching these?

768
00:59:44,831 --> 00:59:45,832
No problem.

769
00:59:45,915 --> 00:59:47,333
-Thank you.
-Go ahead.

770
00:59:47,417 --> 00:59:48,585
Thank you very much, sir.

771
00:59:56,593 --> 00:59:58,094
Hey, why don't we try these?

772
00:59:59,721 --> 01:00:00,847
These look good.

773
01:00:02,724 --> 01:00:03,808
-Excuse me?
-Yes.

774
01:00:03,891 --> 01:00:05,602
-Could we have some sweet potatoes?
-Sure.

775
01:00:05,685 --> 01:00:06,769
Good morning.

776
01:00:06,853 --> 01:00:08,688
Oh, my, you brought
a girlfriend this time?

777
01:00:08,771 --> 01:00:11,149
Oh, goodness!

778
01:00:11,232 --> 01:00:13,693
You look like such a sweet couple.

779
01:00:13,776 --> 01:00:15,403
Oh, we're…

780
01:00:16,279 --> 01:00:18,489
-Thank you.
-Why aren't you saying anything?

781
01:00:19,407 --> 01:00:20,408
Almost ready.

782
01:00:22,035 --> 01:00:24,579
-That will be 8,000 won.
-Oh, thank you. Put them here.

783
01:00:24,662 --> 01:00:26,539
-Here.
-Thank you.

784
01:00:26,623 --> 01:00:28,499
-Potatoes?
-Yeah, just a few will do.

785
01:00:28,583 --> 01:00:29,584
All right.

786
01:00:30,501 --> 01:00:32,086
You look so happy, kid.

787
01:00:32,837 --> 01:00:34,255
That's 13,000 won.

788
01:00:34,339 --> 01:00:35,340
Thirteen thousand, huh?

789
01:00:35,423 --> 01:00:36,716
I'll give you a discount.

790
01:00:36,799 --> 01:00:39,344
And thank her.
I like her, she's so pretty.

791
01:00:39,427 --> 01:00:41,888
-Ten thousand will do.
-Thank you, ma'am.

792
01:00:41,971 --> 01:00:43,973
-Such a pretty girl.
-Here you go.

793
01:00:44,891 --> 01:00:47,185
-You got a discount 'cause of me.
-I'll cook something nice.

794
01:00:47,268 --> 01:00:49,228
-Thank you, bye.
-Thank you.

795
01:00:49,812 --> 01:00:51,064
It's so pretty.

796
01:00:51,147 --> 01:00:52,231
How much for the flowers?

797
01:00:52,315 --> 01:00:54,484
Those? Twenty-three thousand.

798
01:00:54,567 --> 01:00:56,486
-These are 23,000?
-Yep.

799
01:00:56,569 --> 01:00:58,363
-We'll get some.
-Okay.

800
01:00:59,614 --> 01:01:00,782
-Wait.
-What?

801
01:01:00,865 --> 01:01:03,034
Thank you, we'll just come back next time.

802
01:01:09,040 --> 01:01:11,000
Looks like it's broken.

803
01:01:12,752 --> 01:01:15,713
Oh, Do-hyeok, what did you do?

804
01:01:15,797 --> 01:01:17,924
-I didn't do anything.
-Jeez. Look at this.

805
01:01:18,007 --> 01:01:20,426
Oh! Hey, Na-bi.

806
01:01:22,804 --> 01:01:25,139
Wow, is this really our Na-bi?

807
01:01:26,349 --> 01:01:28,017
-Who is…
-Oh, sorry.

808
01:01:28,101 --> 01:01:29,435
I guess you don't remember her.

809
01:01:29,519 --> 01:01:31,437
She's my cousin, Do-yeon.

810
01:01:33,231 --> 01:01:37,151
Oh, I see. Yeah, Do-yeon.

811
01:01:37,235 --> 01:01:38,403
It's been a long time.

812
01:01:38,486 --> 01:01:41,823
-Wow, you really are unbelievable.
-Don't say anything weird.

813
01:01:41,906 --> 01:01:44,242
What? I'm surprised! She looks so pretty!

814
01:01:44,325 --> 01:01:46,202
-That's true.
-No.

815
01:01:46,285 --> 01:01:48,496
You're all grown up.
I didn't recognize you.

816
01:01:49,205 --> 01:01:51,916
By the way, your bike, it's broken.
And you have a flat.

817
01:01:51,999 --> 01:01:54,377
-You better not ride it.
-Oh, did I break the bike?

818
01:01:54,460 --> 01:01:55,503
Oh, no, no.

819
01:01:55,586 --> 01:01:58,256
Someone must have messed it up
while we were shopping.

820
01:01:58,339 --> 01:02:01,134
-Let's go get it fixed.
-Mm.

821
01:02:01,217 --> 01:02:02,468
No need for that.

822
01:02:02,552 --> 01:02:04,262
I mean, you can ride on one together.

823
01:02:04,345 --> 01:02:06,764
While I have this broken one fixed.

824
01:02:09,642 --> 01:02:11,936
Go on. Oh, come on. You two go ahead.

825
01:02:12,520 --> 01:02:13,646
See you guys!

826
01:02:14,897 --> 01:02:17,567
-See you later, Do-yeon.
-Thank you!

827
01:02:31,456 --> 01:02:32,498
What's that?

828
01:02:33,708 --> 01:02:35,835
Oh, I just want you to be comfortable.

829
01:02:42,884 --> 01:02:44,010
Get on.

830
01:02:56,022 --> 01:02:57,148
Let's go.

831
01:03:21,672 --> 01:03:24,091
So, are you going to sleep over
with your friends?

832
01:03:24,175 --> 01:03:26,844
No, I'm staying at my aunt's,
maybe drop by, or whatever.

833
01:03:27,470 --> 01:03:30,515
Okay. I'll just take you home, then.
I have something to tell you.

834
01:03:30,598 --> 01:03:31,891
What is it?

835
01:03:31,974 --> 01:03:33,267
Relax, I'll tell you later.

836
01:03:51,786 --> 01:03:54,038
Hey, where do you want me
to put all these?

837
01:03:54,121 --> 01:03:56,958
Over there. You know what?
I'll take care of those.

838
01:04:43,921 --> 01:04:46,674
Hey, how are you? I'm Park Jae-eon.

839
01:04:48,217 --> 01:04:49,969
I'm good, how are you? I'm Yang Do-hyeok.

840
01:05:51,822 --> 01:05:53,324
How have you been?

841
01:05:53,407 --> 01:05:56,494
-Mm. So-so.
-Haven't been doing so well.

842
01:05:56,577 --> 01:06:00,498
That familiar intoxicating scent
has come to haunt me once more.

843
01:06:00,581 --> 01:06:01,540
He is charming.

844
01:06:01,624 --> 01:06:03,626
Now, if you went after him,
I wouldn't mind at all.

845
01:06:03,709 --> 01:06:05,670
For some reason,
those two look like newlyweds.

846
01:06:05,753 --> 01:06:08,172
To be honest,
Na-bi really is my first love.

847
01:06:08,255 --> 01:06:11,217
What's your relationship to Jae-eon?
Are you two close?

848
01:06:11,300 --> 01:06:13,094
There's nothing between us.

849
01:06:13,886 --> 01:06:16,722
I kept thinking about you.
I've missed you more than you'll know.

850
01:06:16,806 --> 01:06:18,224
You already have a girlfriend.

851
01:06:18,307 --> 01:06:19,141
Is that the issue?

852
01:06:19,225 --> 01:06:21,394
I think it's about time
you stop playing games with me.

853
01:06:21,477 --> 01:06:23,020
It's time for us to end this.

854
01:06:23,104 --> 01:06:24,397
-Stop it.
-What?

855
01:06:24,480 --> 01:06:26,273
-This whole thing.
-Where's Na-bi?

856
01:06:26,357 --> 01:06:28,526
-She's too tired to come.
-She's not coming?

857
01:06:28,609 --> 01:06:31,445
All you have to do is tell me
that you don't want any of this.
